so many cute girls

00:20:39.447 --> 00:20:41.074 position:50% align:center
to talk to you when
you walk around campus?

00:20:41.157 --> 00:20:42.659 position:50% align:center
Yeah! Cause the one
that came up to you

00:20:42.742 --> 00:20:46.037 position:50% align:center
while we were in the cafeteria
yesterday was exactly my type.

00:20:46.121 --> 00:20:48.415 position:50% align:center
Please introduce us.

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:52.043 position:50% align:center
Try to keep it in
your pants, kid.

00:20:52.127 --> 00:20:54.254 position:50% align:center
Hey. It isn't our
fault that Ibuki

00:20:54.337 --> 00:20:56.423 position:50% align:center
never wants to hook us up
with any hotties.

00:20:56.506 --> 00:20:58.550 position:50% align:center
