All that snake cares about

00:20:58.633 --> 00:21:00.552 position:50% align:center
is hogging the spotlight
when he should be sharing!

00:21:00.635 --> 00:21:04.431 position:50% align:center
That isn't the point.
You two. What was that about?

00:21:04.514 --> 00:21:06.766 position:50% align:center
I apologize.

00:21:06.850 --> 00:21:08.309 position:50% align:center
Now your turn.

00:21:08.393 --> 00:21:09.519 position:50% align:center
Bite me.

00:21:09.602 --> 00:21:12.147 position:50% align:center
[IKUTO] You wanna maybe
try that again? Huh?

00:21:12.230 --> 00:21:14.524 position:50% align:center
[NATSUSA] Give me another
chance, please! Ow, ow...

00:21:14.607 --> 00:21:15.692 position:50% align:center
You wouldn't think it,

00:21:15.775 --> 00:21:18.028 position:50% align:center
but that kid really enjoys
picking a fight.

00:21:18.111 --> 00:21:20.030 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it's in his DNA.

00:21:20.113 --> 00:21:22.073 position:50% align:center
How do you deal?

00:21:22.157 --> 00:21:25.160 position:50% align:center
Well, Natsu's typically
the one who does the dealing.

00:21:25.243 --> 00:21:26.828 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:21:27.912 --> 00:21:30.498 position:50% align:center
[IBUKI] He protected me.
Ever since we were little kids,

00:21:30.582 --> 00:21:33.043 position:50% align:center
he's stood up for me
like a tiny soldier.

00:21:33.126 --> 00:21:37.756 position:50% align:center
Always made sure I never had
a reason to lose my head.

00:21:37.839 --> 00:21:41.384 position:50% align:center
[yelling]

00:21:41.468 --> 00:21:43.428 position:50% align:center
[IBUKI]
On the flip side...

00:21:43.511 --> 00:21:46.806 position:50% align:center
I get 13 times the abuse
that anybody else does.

00:21:46.890 --> 00:21:49.642 position:50% align:center
That's an oddly
specific number.

00:21:54.564 --> 00:21:59.069 position:50% align:center
[sighs] Should be
the last one. Nice.

00:21:59.152 --> 00:22:00.653 position:50% align:center
[YUU gasps]

00:22:02.447 --> 00:22:05.033 position:50% align:center
Uh, I'm sorry.

